Updates the fields of this FEMContactPairs object. If one or more fields are specified, only the fields listed will be updated, the other fields will be left unchanged. If the field list is empty ALL fields will be updated. The available fields are:

  • ContactorSurf
  • ContGroupID
  • ContPair
  • FContactor
  • Friction
  • FTarget
  • HeatTransf
  • RecordNmb
  • TargetSurf
  • TBirth
  • TDeath
